@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2980B9
  FontColor #1A1A2E
  FontStyle bold
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
  BorderColor #F0C040
  FontColor #333333
}

skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #EAF7EA
  BorderColor #27AE60
}

title <b>Multi-Agent Pipeline: Optimal Context-Passing Strategy</b>\n<size:11>Coordinator passes Synthesis Draft + Structured Source Index to Report Generator</size>

actor "User" as User

box "Agent Pipeline" #F0F4FF
  participant "Web Search\nAgent" as WSA
  participant "Document Analysis\nAgent" as DAA
  participant "Synthesis\nAgent" as SA
  participant "Coordinator" as COORD
  participant "Report Generation\nAgent" as RGA
end box

database "Source Index\n(Structured)" as SI

== Phase 1: Web Search ==

User -> WSA : Research request
activate WSA
WSA -> WSA : Crawl & retrieve sources
note right of WSA
  **Output:**
  25 sources
  ~120K tokens raw content
end note
WSA --> COORD : Raw content + source URLs
deactivate WSA

== Phase 2: Document Analysis ==

COORD -> DAA : Forward raw content (120K tokens)
activate DAA
DAA -> DAA : Extract key insights\nfrom raw sources
note right of DAA
  **Output:**
  Key insights
  ~15K tokens
end note
DAA --> COORD : Extracted insights + claim-source mappings
deactivate DAA

== Phase 3: Synthesis ==

COORD -> SA : Forward extracted insights (15K tokens)
activate SA
SA -> SA : Produce coherent\nnarrative draft
note right of SA
  **Output:**
  Narrative draft
  ~3K tokens
end note
SA --> COORD : Synthesis draft
deactivate SA

== Phase 4: Build Structured Source Index ==

COORD -> SI : Compile source index\nfrom DAA claim-source mappings
activate SI
note over SI
  **Source Index Structure:**
  ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
  │ claim_id  → source_url + excerpt    │
  │ claim_id  → source_url + excerpt    │
  │ ...                                 │
  └─────────────────────────────────────┘
  Maps each key claim in the draft
  to its origin URL and relevant snippet.
  Avoids re-reading 120K tokens.
end note
SI --> COORD : Structured source index (~compact)
deactivate SI

== Phase 5: Optimal Context Hand-off ✅ ==

COORD -> RGA : **Synthesis Draft (3K tokens)**\n+ **Structured Source Index**
activate RGA

note over COORD, RGA #D5F5E3
  ✅ **Optimal Strategy:**
  Pass synthesis draft + source index
  ——————————————————————————
  ✔ Narrative gives the story & structure
  ✔ Source index binds claims → citations
  ✔ No need to re-read 120K raw tokens
  ✔ Completeness + efficiency balanced
end note

RGA -> RGA : Generate final report\nwith proper citations
note right of RGA
  **Uses:**
  • Draft → narrative structure
  • Source index → inline citations
  • Does NOT re-read raw content
end note
RGA --> User : Final Report\n(with cited sources)
deactivate RGA

== ❌ Rejected Strategies (for contrast) ==

note over COORD #FFE0E0
  ❌ Pass all 120K raw tokens → token overload, inefficient
  ❌ Pass only synthesis draft → no citation binding possible
  ❌ Pass only source URLs → agent must re-fetch & re-read
  ❌ Pass extracted insights only → loses narrative coherence
end note

@enduml

